Dear Judge Parker, 
Attached for the Court's consideration, please find an amended application and amended affidavit in support of a second 
warrant and order. As detailed in the amended application and amended affidavit, this afternoon, realized 
that she had inadvertently included two errors in the affidavit submitted to Your Honor yesterday. Accordingly, the 
Government respectfully submits these amended materials and requests the issuance of a second warrant and order. 
If at all possible, we would be extremely grateful if the agent could please swear out this warrant today. I can be reached 
at and the agent can be available at any time convenient for the Court. We apologize for the error and the 
inconvenience. 
Respectfully submitted, 
Assistant United States Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
1  St. Andrew's Plaza 
New York, NY 10007 
EFTA00026524
